videos.description: Penn State's Grant Haley intercepts Pittsburgh's Max Browne to set up the Nittany Lions with great field position
videos.headline: Penn State's defense starts strong

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley finds Mike Gesicki in the end zone to give the Nittany Lions an early 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: Penn State on the board quickly

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley runs for 36 yards to give the Nittany Lions a first down.
videos.headline: McSorley uses feet to get the first down

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley and Mike Gesicki combine for their second touchdown of the game against Pittsburgh.
videos.headline: McSorley and Gesicki connect for second TD

videos.description: Penn State's Troy Apke intercepts Pittsburgh's Max Browne, giving the Nittany Lions their second interception of the game.
videos.headline: Penn State's defense forces second INT

videos.description: Pittsburgh's Dewayne Hendrix sacks Penn State's Trace McSorley for a loss of seven yards.
videos.headline: Pittsburgh sacks McSorley for a loss of seven

videos.description: Pittsburgh head coach Pat Narduzzi speaks highly of his defense's ability to stop the high-powered Penn State offense.
videos.headline: Narduzzi praises defense for stifling PSU

videos.description: Penn State's Saquon Barkley gets things rolling for the Nittany Lions with a 17-yard run to start the third quarter.
videos.headline: Barkley sparks offense in the third quarter

videos.description: Penn State's Saquon Barkley catches a pass from Trace McSorley and cruises downfield for the 46-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Barkley shows off speed with TD catch-and-run

videos.description: Pittsburgh's Qadree Ollison shows off his strength by muscling through defenders for a 32-yard run.
videos.headline: Pitt's Ollison muscles for first down on big run

videos.description: Penn State's Saquon Barkley powers through the Pittsburgh defense for the 8-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Barkley 'lowers the boom' for the TD

videos.description: Penn State's Nick Scott picks up Pittsburgh's Darrin Hall and slams him to the ground for the tackle.
videos.headline: Penn State picks up ball carrier for the tackle

videos.description: Pittsburgh's Ben Dinucci jukes into the end zone for the touchdown to bring the Panthers within two scores.
videos.headline: Pittsburgh cuts into Penn State's lead

videos.description: Penn State's DaeSean Hamilton tips the ball to himself to give the Nittany Lions a first down on a 23-yard catch.
videos.headline: Penn State makes amazing bobbling catch

videos.description: Penn State's Marcus Allen tackles Pittsburgh's Darrin Hall in the end zone for a safety.
videos.headline: Penn State pushes Pittsburgh back for safety

videos.description: Penn State running back Saquon Barkley talks about 'tremendous' defense as the Nittany Lions take down Pittsburgh 33-14.
videos.headline: Barkley praises strong defense

videos.headline: Saquon Barkley shines against Pittsburgh
